        "richtext_YNRL3z": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>This isn’t your typical workspace. Grab a day pass and post up with your laptop—we’ve got strong WiFi and stronger coffee. Knock out calls, then shift gears. Goat yoga in the morning. Technogym workout or a lift in the barn. Infrared sauna. Hyperbaric chamber. Or go full send: 230°F sauna, 35°F plunge. Reset your nervous system. Feed a baby cow. Saddle up and ride a horse. Grab fresh food, meet real people, and breathe clean air. This place is built for founders, creatives, and operators who need space to think, move, and reconnect.</p>",
            "text_size": 20,
            "text_bottom_spacing": 20
