          "settings": {
            "question": "What are the farm's hours?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Sweet Honey Farm is open daily, Monday through Sunday. However, some dates may be unavailable for Day Pass guests due to private events. </p><p><strong>Spring/Summer Hours</strong><br/></p><p>Entire Property</p><ul><li>Mon–Tue: 10 AM–6 PM</li><li>Wed–Fri: 10 AM–8 PM</li><li>Sat–Sun: 10 AM–3 PM</li></ul><p>The Farmstand</p><ul><li>Mon–Sun: 10 AM–3 PM</li></ul><p>The Farmstand Meals</p><ul><li>10:30 AM–11:30 AM</li><li> 1:30 PM–3 PM</li><li>12 PM–2 PM (soup, bone broth, and build-your-own salads available)</li></ul>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_content_nCqJgM": {
          "type": "tab_content",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I check in?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Head to The Farmhouse and enter through the red French doors. A team member at the front desk will check you in and help you complete a waiver.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_content_wC9QjG": {
          "type": "tab_content",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What’s included with a Day Pass?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<ul><li>Full access to all fitness, wellness, and recovery amenities</li><li>Participation in one scheduled workout class (or open gym access if no class is running)</li><li>One farm-fresh meal (choose breakfast or lunch at check-in)</li><li>Guided property tours available upon request</li><li>Complimentary WiFi throughout the grounds</li></ul><p><em>Bonus: If you become a member after your visit, you’ll receive a $250 credit toward your membership.</em><br/></p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_content_YeBJDi": {
          "type": "tab_content",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What should I wear?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We recommend comfortable activewear, workout clothes, and closed-toe shoes. Don’t forget a bathing suit for the sauna or cold plunge, plus sunscreen and a hat for sunny days.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "tab_content_dLfGDy": {
          "type": "tab_content",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I have a dietary restriction—what should I do?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Just let us know when you check in. Our on-site chef will be happy to accommodate your needs.</p>",
